System and packages used to build NMFSReports

April 27 2022

Source: vignettes/E_thispkgwasbuiltusing.Rmd
E_thispkgwasbuiltusing.Rmd
library(NMFSReports)

This vignette does not contain any examples of using NMF Reports, specifically, but does record what packges and system is ws built on. See below:
